=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess/cn2HlVtNgQM/oTGCvrdcJ0gJ\">PGN and other related Issues. POINTS ARISING</a> by Mark Crowther, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgc</a>, July 29, 1994</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/rec.games.chess.computer/0-xpXHbfzh4/GoKIkW0SKoUJ\">Help on PGN/ EPD-Format and its implementation wanted</a> by <a href=\"/Rudolf_Posch\" title=\"Rudolf Posch\">Rudolf Posch</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, November 05, 1996</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Portable_Game_Notation&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=112889\">Replacing PGN with XML?</a> by <a href=\"/Thorsten_Greiner\" title=\"Thorsten Greiner\">Thorsten Greiner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 29, 2000  <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=138460\">File name extensions</a> by <a href=\"/Leen_Ammeraal\" title=\"Leen Ammeraal\">Leen Ammeraal</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 14, 2000 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://groups.google.com/group/rec.games.chess.computer/browse_frm/thread/16d5281457cd5df4/f69f034f01ca3d32\">PGN update and revisions</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Edwards\" title=\"Steven Edwards\">Steven Edwards</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">rgcc</a>, May 21, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=